  <h2>Personal Statement</h2>
  <p>Hello, I'm Keeghan McGarry, originally from New Zealand, now enjoying life in Liverpool, England. At heart, I'm a tech enthusiast, chess aficionado, and an imaginative Dungeons & Dragons storyteller. My journey in technology spans over a decade, starting in software engineering and gradually moving to roles where technology meets human interaction.</p>
